{"tid":2455921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【緬甸政變】示威者網上睇片學槍械射擊　擬自組軍隊對抗軍政府","createTime":"2021-03-21T13:32:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T02:13:02.000Z","uid":261647,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a480c640faa657bafa731b5b5b8aaf8345f0d05b","tid":2455921,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:32:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/緬甸政變-示威者網上睇片學槍械射擊-擬自組軍隊對抗軍政府/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87%E5%AD%B8%E6%A7%8D%E6%A2%B0%E5%B0%84%E6%93%8A-%E6%93%AC%E8%87%AA%E7%B5%84%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E8%BB%8D%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%2F&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=2cbcbf0e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E6%94%BF%E8%AE%8A-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9D%87%E7%89%87%E5%AD%B8%E6%A7%8D%E6%A2%B0%E5%B0%84%E6%93%8A-%E6%93%AC%E8%87%AA%E7%B5%84%E8%BB%8D%E9%9A%8A%E5%B0%8D%E6%8A%97%E8%BB%8D%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%2F&h=4afc8d64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/緬甸政變-示威者網上睇片學槍械射擊-擬自組軍隊對抗軍政府/</a><br />\n<br />\n「回望我拍下的片段，我能回顧這場抗爭如何由和平示威，逐漸轉變為生命犧牲。這比任何電影更超現實（surreal）。」某緬甸製片人向《BBC》如是說。緬甸反政變示威持續逾月，軍方連場血腥鎮壓，惟民眾依然上街反抗。《衛報》引述示威者稱，當地年輕人正透過 YouTube 學習整理槍械及射擊，成立「人民軍隊（people&rsquo;s army）」以保護平民的呼聲亦逐漸壯大。<br />\n<br />\n網民無懼討論成立聯邦軍     示威者：人民軍將成為新國防軍<br />\n<br />\n據《衛報》周六（20日）報道，即使軍方封網令市民溝通困難，但不少人仍在 Facebook 匿名討論，民族武裝組織參與反政變示威的重要性。不少網民更呼籲，遭逐出的議員應建立能結束軍方政權的聯邦軍隊（federal army）。一個盾牌狀的軍隊標誌甚至在網上廣泛流傳，按照該圖片說明，標誌的 14 顆星代表緬甸的地區、省份；7 條紅線則代表軍隊秉持的信念，包括政治中立（political impartiality）、保護及服務人民等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWhgdqV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWhgdqV.png&h=b55b658c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n29歲示威者 Zaw 向《衛報》表示，他們不再盼望聯合國或任何軍隊會前來幫助當地民眾，「我們應有一支囊括所有少數族裔的聯邦軍&hellip;&hellip;人民軍將成為新國防軍（Tatmadaw）。」另一名 30 歲示威者 Hlaing 則指，「我們（當地市民）再不需要這支當權軍隊或警隊，我相信將來一場內戰能足以清除他們。」<br />\n<br />\n據報有最少兩個民族武裝組織正協助匿藏逃離政權的政客、公務員、記者等；由全國民主聯盟成員組成的文人平行政府「緬甸聯邦議會代表委員會」（CRPH)則正與數個民族武裝組織會面，並呼籲市民保衛自己。"},{"pid":"e336ce038e3676a72093b02c627480ea5f31010f","tid":2455921,"uid":3297,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"槍係邊到嚟？香港都需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe20696bab1a9e6f963647595202dd1f089aa83","tid":2455921,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e336ce038e3676a72093b02c627480ea5f31010f","tid":2455921,"uid":3297,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"槍係邊到嚟？香港都需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />